      <title>书摘｜光幻中的论语</title>
      <link>https://colarxu.github.io/posts/2023/%E4%B9%A6%E6%91%98%E5%85%89%E5%B9%BB%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%AD/</link>
